    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/bdabb27d0c593ec938987dffcddff7c2.poster.avif?t=1703253063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/bdabb27d0c593ec938987dffcddff7c2.webm?t=1703253063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/bdabb27d0c593ec938987dffcddff7c2.mp4?t=1703253063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从零开始设计<br>从零开始设计，利用蓝图满足您的客户的所有需求。根据他们的要求，打造美丽的客厅、卧室和厨房，欣赏他们对您的作品赞叹不已！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/55a7100524c47f7c64cf5cf6ed9ec7fb.poster.avif?t=1703253063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/55a7100524c47f7c64cf5cf6ed9ec7fb.webm?t=1703253063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/55a7100524c47f7c64cf5cf6ed9ec7fb.mp4?t=1703253063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>玩Blast关卡<br>通过玩Blast关卡，保持您的思维活跃。您不仅可以从游戏中获得乐趣，还可以赢取金币来装饰房屋并在游戏中取得进步。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/bb127a493a8cdf4abecf339078e49b02.poster.avif?t=1703253063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/bb127a493a8cdf4abecf339078e49b02.webm?t=1703253063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/bb127a493a8cdf4abecf339078e49b02.mp4?t=1703253063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>选择合适的家具<br>在为客户的家挑选家具时，花时间探索多种设计，看看哪种最符合他们的风格。通过将三种不同的设计并排进行比较，确保您选择的家具正是您所期望的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/72d496e20d77f67fc4634efadacf48a8.poster.avif?t=1703253063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/72d496e20d77f67fc4634efadacf48a8.webm?t=1703253063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367560/extras/72d496e20d77f67fc4634efadacf48a8.mp4?t=1703253063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>关注故事<br>在创建设计时，要注意客户的故事。例如，Luke希望找到舒适轻松的东西；Ben和Debbie则希望建立一个温馨的家庭巢穴；Anna想让她的地方对朋友们充满吸引力，毕竟她是歌手、词曲创作人、模特和剧作家！",
